description:
Smith is that hot, all-American jock that everybody wants to get to know…in more ways than one!

Keeping that in mind, he also has a humble side to him that makes him ever more attractive than he already is. His “assets” are a major plus, too…especially that ass!

“The butt is the new chest. It’s kind of what everyone looks at now.”

Well, we’re definitely looking at yours, Smith!
title: Smith
